description: Full planning permission for the erection of 4 buildings ranging from 6 to 18 storeys in height, comprising a total of 342 residential dwellings and 1024 sqm Gross Internal Area (GIA) of A1, A4, B1 and/or D1 floorspace, together with access, servicing, car parking, cycle parking, cycle storage, plant, open space and landscaping (amendment to previous approval reference 14/00422/FUL as varied by Section 73 planning permission reference 17/00669/VAR).
